Geeked (https://github.com/Kali99xx/Geeked) is currently closed-source. Whether Geeked will be open sourced and the strategy around it if so, are both still a work in progress.
We're having a discussion on open sourcing Geeked, possible licenses, and also the business model in [GitHub discussion #400](https://github.com/Kali99xx/Geeked/discussions/400)
